{"tid":1520450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武唔好再話要保護和理非唔走","createTime":"2019-08-30T20:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T06:04:39.000Z","uid":265416,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e242d0c13de55ee3e42f0459a515bf089054add8","tid":1520450,"uid":265416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T20:31:17.000Z","msg":"兩個原因<br />\n<br />\n一，後排遠少少已經<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">睇唔到前面發生咩事</span></span>，知道前排有衝突時分分鐘已經短兵相接<br />\n<br />\n二，而家風氣係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">後排唔可以無端端徹走</span></span>，如果唔係前排會落單好危險<br />\n<br />\n最後就後排望前排同狗對峙唔敢走，前排望後排留守唔敢退，最後換黎清場局面<br />\n<br />\n唔好旨意後排手足識得走，你睇下條物資人鏈，次次都係前面指揮後面褪位，後面幾可主動企鬆啲就前面？（唔係話後面d人，意思係後面唔知前面有咁嘅需要）<br />\n<br />\n所以我懇請勇武手足，適當時候<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">主動少少叫後面準備徹離</span></span>，未知其他前排手足有咩決定<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">主動開口問下</span></span>，最好set roadblock之前<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可以有進退共識</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割席，不分化<br />\n現場自決，拒絕送頭</span></span>"},{"pid":"c16b71f50cc98a72c9d1ba2a2315072a2dcc72fc","tid":1520450,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T20:31:34.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會 港島見<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2fQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=380fa4bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2fQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=510ff113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 宣傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2fQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=a60f1cd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">三罷 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FT.me%2Fhkgeneralstrike9293&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2fQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=f7d44b43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293</a></span>"},{"pid":"31a6afcac6ed1b07fc09df97c67bc376d6b7b8dd","tid":1520450,"uid":86442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T21:31:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab7cd12927624ac69b4b49a7443ef022a943fd4c","tid":1520450,"uid":251292,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T21:39:57.000Z","msg":"Agger<br />\n你又係到等和理非<br />\n和理非又係到等你<br />\n一體架喇<br />\n係走就一齊啦<br />\n唔好再成日櫈波鐘"},{"pid":"bfe8530e2f3d8117f55136dc911cd41b485efba4","tid":1520450,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T22:03:57.000Z","msg":"希望今日香港中區無暴徒出現啦<br />\n要暴去其他地區咪仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgm